T1  - Who Owns What? A Factor Model for Direct Stockholding
AU  - BALASUBRAMANIAM, VIMAL
AU  - CAMPBELL, JOHN Y.
AU  - RAMADORAI, TARUN
AU  - RANISH, BENJAMIN
Y1  - 2023/06/01
